The paper deals with the problem of leader election in a network, which is a distributed computing problem. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also involves the use of algorithms and models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.PL (Programming Languages). The use of abstraction and model checking techniques indicates that it could also belong to cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
